      <bpmn2:userTask id="_20504197-0C32-48E3-B308-80C1AAB4D964" name="Configure Derivation Rules (Optional)">
        <bpmn2:documentation><![CDATA[We can optionally configure which BIRD derived attibutes to enable when we create the phsical database, and what the exectable version should look like. Here we try to convert from published psuedo code for derivation transformation rules.]]></bpmn2:documentation>
